            "question": "Can I access myduke® support if I live in a remote area?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. The myduke digital platform is designed to provide structured smoking cessation support to adults across Australia. The online assessment and clinical review process enable people in regional or remote locations to receive guidance from registered healthcare professionals.</p>"
